title: Microsoft Office ProPlus 2007 SP3 VL x86 en-US February 2016
description:
***************************************************
Microsoft Office ProPlus 2007 SP3 VL x86 en-US February 2016
***************************************************

Includes: Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook, Publisher, Access, InfoPath, Communicator

Release Info

- Language: en-US
- Channel: Volume License
- Version: 12.0.6607.1000
- File format: DAA (ISO compressed)
- Includes all updates published till February 9, 2016

Installation

- Unzip ProPlus12.x86.SP3.en-US-2016.02
- If you know how to handle DAA files, just go ahead
- If you don't: run the batch file Makeiso (this will convert the DAA file to ISO and delete intermediary files)
- Mount or burn ISO file and install Office
- Install Office 2007 using one of the provided keys in key.txt
- Install Office File Validation + Visual Studio for Office Runtime (required) from folder "Run after install"
- Customize your installation with included Add-ins: Classic Menu for Office 2007 v7.50, FileFormatConverters, PowerPointViewer, SaveAsPDFandXPS, Wordview

Please SEED for a while!
